===Verb===
'''to wriggle''' ('''wriggles''', '''wriggled''', '''wriggling''')
#''(intransitive)'' to [[slight]]ly [[twist]] one's [[body]] and [[quick]]ly move one's [[limb]]s
#:''Teachers often lose their patience when children '''wriggle''' in their seats.''
